  "title": "🎓 (NO EXP NEEDED) CAMPAIGN MANAGEMENT TRAINEE 🎓",
  "description": "<h2>🗣️ Develop your communication & leadership skills this 2026‼️<br /></h2><p>Altius Organisation is a company appointed by local and international clients from diversified industries to <strong>build their marketing presence and services.</strong></p><p>We are seeking a <strong>driven and ambitious</strong> Campaign Management Trainee to join our sales and marketing team!</p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Acquire and implement strategies to expand consumer base</li><li>Leading team and sales projects to meet client objectives</li><li>Oversee the performance of marketing events and outreach</li><li>Review the effectiveness of strategies according to campaign targets</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Goal-oriented and process-driven mentality</li><li>Self-motivated with a creative character</li><li>A business mindset, passion for achieving as part of an excelling team</li><li>Attitude to contribute and develop alongside the company</li></ul><p></p><p>If you are looking forward to working with some of the leading establishments in the international market, here is your opportunity to <strong>kickstart a career in the sales and marketing field! APPLY NOW ‼️</strong></p>",
